new-album-mountainhead-and-2024-uk-tour-buy-tickets-preorder-3522070">去年春天，他们在英国巡回演出</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/everything-everything-announce-autumn-2024-uk-tour-3789176">在冬季开始了另一回合</a>。上个月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">该小组在英国巡回演出中支持了袋鼠</a>。</p><p>今年夏天，一切都将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-queens-of-the-stone-age-vampire-weekend-to-headline-victorious-festival-2025-line-up-buy-tickets-3818197">胜利的节日</a>，哈德威克节，布莱顿在海滩上和电气湾节上露面。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/everything-everything-announce-get-to-heaven-10th-anniversary-uk-and-ireland-2025-tour-3851970">所有内容宣布“到达天堂” 10周年英国和爱尔兰2025年巡回演出</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
