 by an ancient deity known as Sleep, who promised him &#39;glory and magnificence&#39; if Vessel were to follow him. Each of Sleep Token&#39;s songs are said to be dedicated to this deity, while their sound is just as intriguing: splicing tuned-down tech-metal with the lighter elements of pop and R&amp;B to create a soundscape that&#39;s not only heavy, but curiously accessible.”</p><p>即使在Arcadia中”将于5月9日通过RCA下降，并且可以<a href="https://www.sleep-token.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订</a>。上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/sleep-token-emergence-new-single-review-lost-in-arcadia-3845834"><em>NME</em>对“出现”进行了四星级的评论</a>，并被描述为表现出乐队的“散布，不同的类型的最佳”。</p><p>它写道：“在六分钟26秒的时间里，它表明乐队现在似乎越来越害怕执行这些漫长而蜿蜒的曲目，这些曲目在流派之间毫不费力地切换。” </p><figure id="attachment_3845964" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3845964" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3845964" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270.jpg" alt="睡眠令牌表演现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Sleep-token@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3845964" class="wp-caption-text">睡眠令牌现场表演。学分：Katja Ogrin/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>它补充说：“如果有的话，&#39;出现&#39;确认了他们仍然在商店中拥有的左转弯，并在“即使在阿卡迪亚”上的世界建设范围内保持着阴谋，一些粉丝们期望这会远离以前的专辑三部曲。” “与此同时，我们只能继续进行睡眠代币总是要求我们做的事情：敬拜。”</p><p>睡眠代币将于今年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>和<a href="https://w